<div class="design-holder">
  <p><strong data-toggle="tooltip" title="Hard-coded numbers that are not assigned to a variable.">Magic Number -</strong>
    Your file has <%= @analysis[:MagicNumber][:number] %> magic number(s):
    <ul>
      <% @analysis[:MagicNumber][:name].each do |name| %>
        <li>
          <%= name %>
        </li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
  <p>Magic numbers make it difficult to maintain our code. We should try to have a single place where we define constants etc, then reference this throughout our code. <a class="resource-link" href="https://goo.gl/xTS8ku">Learn how to refactor these magic numbers away!</a>
</div>
